channel.title: TrisidiaX V2! Join Now!
channel.description:
[size=12pt]Hello! I am Trisidia! You might know me from my last release of TrisdiaX and well decided i would want to make an V2![/size] [size=14pt]SO COME JOIN US![/size] [size=12pt]About the RsPs[/size]
Revision: 317 Owner: Trisidia Moderators: Angel, Mystogan Website Developer: Kanu
[size=17pt]Well the Crew i could get is a Php Coder, and an Html coder, maybe a spare Java Coder wouldnt help![/size]
[size=18pt]Well there are Thousands of Rsps out there! Why join TrisidiaX!?[/size]
[size=14pt]We have a Stablized Eco! All dupes either patched or disabled! Added in a new KillStreak system Active Staff Added in new Level Point System with a shop added to use those points! Great Xp Rate (A few skills xp rate are being changed) Server on an Auto Save No Lagg! Own Webclient! Not many custom items! (Custom Items = LAG!) Pk has been advanced and more fun Has awesome shops! And a lot more! THESE ARE WHAT I LOVE ABOUT THE RSPS :D[/size]
[size=19pt]Well here are some pictures![/size]
[size=15pt]We have this awesome Level Point shop! LVL UP for the items![/size]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/u/91577463/Pictures/Level%20Point%20Shop.png[/img]
[size=15pt]Here is the new Pk KillStreak Point System![/size]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/u/91577463/Pictures/New%20Ks%20point%20system.png[/img]
[size=15pt]This is my version of the SOF! FOR Donators ONLY![/size]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/u/91577463/Pictures/The%20new%20SOF.png[/img]
[size=15pt]Come and join the fun![/size]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/u/91577463/Pictures/Come%20Join%21.png[/img]
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ [size=13pt]Well! hope we can see you there! Website:[/size] [size=20pt][url=http://trisidiax.enjin.com]Click Here To Play![/url][/size]
